493}, {\"ngram\": \"the best year\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"Ruud\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He is the No.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 seed, and he has 24 Slams under his belt, so if there is anyone who knows when to find their peak and form, it's probably him.\\\"\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1 seed\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"24 Slams\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"his belt\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"their peak\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic is coming off a loss in the semifinals at the Geneva Open, a lower-tier event that he normally would never enter on the eve of a major.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"a loss\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"the semifinals\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"the Geneva Open\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"a lower-tier event\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the eve\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"a major\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said after that defeat that he had stomach problems.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that defeat\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"stomach problems\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before that came a second-round loss at the Italian Open - and a bizarre episode in which a spectator's water bottle conked him in the head after a match - which was preceded by a semifinal setback against Rudd at Monte Carlo.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\